{"tid":754263,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［GBA][Pokemon] 想搵番一隻game..","createTime":"2018-07-24T09:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T19:00:39.000Z","uid":81137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3af2f8a101c15a9b33f3cd9b9e4587d55deffa66","tid":754263,"uid":81137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T09:17:54.000Z","msg":"大約幾年前，用手機模擬器玩過一隻極高難度既GBA金銀修改版（或者係水晶，唔太記得）。主線除左難度提升之外，基本上都同原版相似。<br />\n<br />\n最好玩係完左主線後有一座極高難度既戰鬥塔，對方每一項努力值都全滿，有神獸，有裝備，招式亦特別配置過。<br />\n<br />\n最記得有隻黑依貝，配猛毒、保護、路釘、月光，裝剩飯 ，屈死我唔少寵，一用鋼系或者格鬥系想打柒佢就轉寵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n忽然想玩番，上網搵唔到，有冇人知邊到有得下載<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bfefd2aa5a6d08ca51706d8915534b99573001e","tid":754263,"uid":81137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T09:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"940c6cd19f55fb794c9f134d58cedd652ff10c20","tid":754263,"uid":81137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T10:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc18a23bf4f50700522edb3c25c961497fc0bc6","tid":754263,"uid":136912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T10:22:46.000Z","msg":"漆黑的魅影？綠寶石改版"},{"pid":"088eeb559436413ec11a73d47f1799af78bf8fda","tid":754263,"uid":81137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bc18a23bf4f50700522edb3c25c961497fc0bc6","tid":754263,"uid":136912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T10:22:46.000Z","msg":"漆黑的魅影？綠寶石改版"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:04:29.000Z","msg":"都好肯定係金銀水晶版黎，因為每項能力都可以255..."},{"pid":"d7f53362d2e375c0d318ab1f154b6db11a2b7406","tid":754263,"uid":81137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:28:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e5e87594270a5c803494bf47746b2c39e164f89d","tid":754263,"ui